{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/register(cancellable:)"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO19ApplicationProtocolPAAE8register11cancellableSbAA14CancellableRefVSg_tKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO14ApplicationRefV","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO","title":"register(cancellable:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"register"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"register"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the point at which the application discovers if it is the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary instance or merely acting as a remote for an already-existing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"primary instance.  This is implemented by attempting to acquire the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"application identifier as a unique bus name on the session bus using","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"GDBus.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If there is no application ID or if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nonUnique"},{"text":" was","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"given, then this process will always become the primary instance."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Due to the internal architecture of GDBus, method calls can be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dispatched at any time (even if a main loop is not running).  For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"this reason, you must ensure that any object paths that you wish to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"register are registered before calling this function.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the application has already been registered then "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returned with no work performed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The [Application](\/\/documentation\/gio\/application\/onstartup(flags:handler:) signal is emitted if registration succeeds"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application"},{"type":"text","text":" is the primary instance (including the non-unique"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"case)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In the event of an error (such as ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being cancelled, or a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"failure to connect to the session bus), "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is returned and ","type":"text"},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is set appropriately.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: the return value of this function is not an indicator that this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"instance is or is not the primary instance of the application.  See","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_application_get_is_remote()"},{"type":"text","text":" for that."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Attempts registration of the application."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref\/register(cancellable:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ApplicationRef","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref","title":"ApplicationRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ApplicationRef"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GApplication"},{"text":" is the core class for application support.","type":"text"}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/applicationref\/applicationprotocol-implementations","type":"topic","title":"ApplicationProtocol Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","abstract":[]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ApplicationRef/register(cancellable:)":{"identifier":"